## Compress directory and save .zip to target_dir:

./backupManager.sh ./target/ ./dir2/ ./target2

## Compress directory and send .zip to target host: (in this example localhost)

./backupManager.sh ./target/ ./dir2/ ./target2

## Compress directory and send .zip to remote host:

./backupManager.sh ./target/ ./dir2/ root@192.168.1.10:/home/rav/backup/